</ul>

<h3>How Often Should You Schedule These Services?</h3>
<p>The frequency of carpet and upholstery care depends on several factors:</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Household Traffic:</strong> High-traffic homes benefit from more frequent services, typically every 6-12 months.</li>
  <li><strong>Pet Owners:</strong> Homes with pets should consider quarterly cleaning to manage fur and dander.</li>
  <li><strong>Allergy Concerns:</strong> Monthly or bi-monthly services can help maintain air quality.</li>
</ul>
<p>In The Shoals & Surrounding Areas, we tailor our services to meet the unique needs of each household, ensuring optimal results.</p>

